OL,3,CHow much could you be owed under car
OL,4,Cloan scandal compensation plans?
OL,6,FCompensation payouts on around 14
OL,7,Fmillion unfair car finance deals could
OL,8,Fstart next year, the Financial Conduct
OL,9,FAuthority (FCA) has said.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, the regulator confirmed
OL,12,Fvictims of the mis-selling of car
OL,13,Ffinance could be owed hundreds of
OL,14,Fpounds through the redress scheme.
OL,16,FThe scheme comes after the FCA found
OL,17,Fmotor finance firms broke the law or
OL,18,Fits rules by not properly informing
OL,19,Fcustomers about commission paid by
OL,20,Flenders to the car dealers that sold
OL,21,Fthem the loan.
