OL,6,FIt believes that setting up a free
OL,7,Fcompensation scheme will be easier and
OL,8,Fquicker for customers to access, and
OL,9,Fmore cost-effective for firms by
OL,10,Fremoving much of the legal and
OL,11,Fadministrative work.
OL,13,FFCA chief executive Nikhil Rathi said:
OL,14,F"Our scheme aims to be simple for
OL,15,Fpeople to use and lenders to implement.
