OL,6,F"We recognise that there will be a
OL,7,Fwide range of views on the scheme, its
OL,8,Fscope, timeframe and how compensation
OL,9,Fis calculated. On such a complex
OL,10,Fissue, not everyone will get
OL,11,Feverything they would like.
OL,13,F"But we want to work together on the
OL,14,Fbest possible scheme and draw a line
OL,15,Funder this issue quickly."
OL,17,FITV News explains how to know if
OL,18,Fyou've been affected, and how much you
OL,19,Fcould be owed.
