OL,3,CHow much could you be owed under car
OL,4,Cloan scandal compensation plans?
OL,6,FThe FCA has said car finance companies
OL,7,Fbroke the rules by not disclosing
OL,8,Finformation, which prevented consumers
OL,9,Ffrom being able to find better deals
OL,10,Felsewhere or negotiate, with some
OL,11,Fpaying more for their loan.
OL,13,FThe scheme covers motor finance
OL,14,Fagreements taken out between April 6
OL,15,F2007 and November 1 2024, where
OL,16,Fcommission was payable by the lender
OL,17,Fto the broker.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
