OL,3,CHow much could you be owed under car
OL,4,Cloan scandal compensation plans?
OL,6,FAccording to the FCA, people would
OL,7,Fonly be able to get compensation if
OL,8,Fthey were not told details of at least
OL,9,Fone of three arrangements:
OL,11,F1. A discretionary commission
OL,12,Farrangement, which allowed the broker
OL,13,Fto adjust the interest rate the
OL,14,Fcustomer would pay to obtain a higher
OL,15,Fcommission.
OL,17,F2. A high commission arrangement (35%
OL,18,Fof the total cost of credit and 10% of
OL,19,Fthe loan).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
