OL,6,F3. A contractual arrangement or tie
OL,7,Fbetween the lender and broker, which
OL,8,Fprovided exclusive or near exclusive
OL,9,Frights to lenders to provide credit.
OL,11,FHow much compensation is available?
OL,13,FAccording to estimates by the FCA,
OL,14,Fpeople would be set to receive around
OL,15,F#700 per agreement on average, with
OL,16,Flenders paying out a possible #8.2
OL,17,Fbillion into the scheme. This is lower
OL,18,Fthan the #9 billion to #18 billion
OL,19,Frange it had previously projected.
OL,21,FWhen could I get the money and how?
