OL,3,CHow much could you be owed under car
OL,4,Cloan scandal compensation plans?
OL,6,FResearch commissioned by the FCA shows
OL,7,Fthat almost half of those aware of
OL,8,Fpossible compensation, but who had not
OL,9,Fyet made a claim (46%) cite a lack of
OL,10,Fclarity on whether a claim would be
OL,11,Feligible as a barrier, and nearly a
OL,12,Fquarter (24%) say uncertainty about
OL,13,Fthe level of compensation makes it
OL,14,Fless likely they would seek
OL,15,Fcompensation.
OL,17,FIf you are worried you were not told
OL,18,Fkey details about your motor finance
OL,19,Farrangement, such as commission
OL,20,Fpayments, the FCA advises submitting a
OL,21,Fcomplaint to your lender.
