OL,3,CHow much could you be owed under car
OL,4,Cloan scandal compensation plans?
OL,6,FA document template for making a
OL,7,Fcomplaint can be found on the
OL,8,Fregulator's website.
OL,10,FLenders will contact those who have
OL,11,Falready complained when the scheme
OL,12,Fgoes live. The FCA has said those who
OL,13,Fhave already complained before this
OL,14,Fpoint are likely to receive
OL,15,Fcompensation faster.
OL,17,FIf you do not submit a complaint, you
OL,18,Fwill be contacted by their lender
OL,19,Fwithin six months of the scheme
OL,20,Fstarting and given the option to opt
OL,21,Fin to it.
